## Credential Handling

On first use each session:
1. Check environment variable `{{SKILL_NAME_UPPER}}_API_KEY`
2. If not set, prompt: "This skill needs a {{Service Name}} API key. Provide it now — held in memory only, never written to disk."
3. Validate with a lightweight API call
4. If validation fails, report error and ask for corrected key

