## Self-Improvement Protocol

After every session:
1. New recipes → add to `references/recipes.md`
2. New patterns → update relevant reference file
3. Bugs found → update `references/known-issues.md`
4. New capabilities → update `USAGE.md`
5. Unexpected behavior → append to `LESSONS-LEARNED.md`
6. Sync to GitHub (verify privacy first)
